Tom:

Per my discussion with you this morning, please coordinate with each of the book administrators (and other appropriate personnel) and explain the process for compilation of the counterparty trading exposure data for the EGM commodity trading businesses. The attachments are the templates for listing the counterparties and corresponding trading exposure data. This approach will put the EGM information on the same playing field with power and gas. This will also help with the forthcoming Ernst & Young/Creditors' Committee discussions about valuations and potential settlements with counterparties.

Alan

